* Tett, P.: ''[https://web.archive.org/web/20051001074904/http://www.lifesciences.napier.ac.uk/teaching/MB/MB9.html Bioluminescence]'', lecture notes from the 1999/2000 edition of that same course. Last accessed 2005-07-18.

